## Start of task

1. `git fetch origin && git pull origin main` (then create `cursor/<name>-1a65`).
2. Read **`docs/CONTEXT.md`** → **`docs/MAINTAINING_DOCS.md`** → **`docs/HANDOFF.md`** → **`AGENTS.md`**.

`config.js` has dev/prod Supabase keys — do not ask the user to paste keys.

Do not use deleted `cursor/multi-game-platform-*` or `cursor/multigame-leib-platform-*` branches. No Firebase.

## End of task (before PR — mandatory)

Follow **`docs/MAINTAINING_DOCS.md`** checklist:

- Update **`docs/CONTEXT.md`** section “Current code (main)”
- Update **`docs/ROADMAP.md`** if you completed roadmap items
- Rewrite **`docs/HANDOFF.md`** with next-agent prompt (use template in MAINTAINING_DOCS.md)
- Copy the “Next agent prompt” from HANDOFF.md into the PR description

Tests: `ln -sf ../leibgame-assets/assets ./assets` then `python3 -m http.server 8000` + `npx playwright test tests/example.spec.js tests/model_load.spec.js tests/clouds_start.spec.js`

Before PR: verify in a real browser (Cursor Cloud desktop or local) — hub → Clouds → play → hub → Clouds again; Start Game must work both times.

Repo docs are the single source of truth — not chat, not wiki-only notes.
